{
  "texts": [
    "By developing such a model, we can better estimate the risk and time frame for developing DR, which would significantly enhance the efficiency of DR screening programs 15.",
    "Furthermore, we can allocate more intensive DR management strategies to those at high risk, which could help prevent the progression of DR.",
    "Artificial intelligence (AI) has been playing an increasingly important role in medicine 2, 16.",
    "Deep learning (DL), with convolutional neural networks, has been developed for the automated detection of DR from retinal photographs [17] [18] [19] [20].",
    "There are, however, very few studies with retinal image-based DL systems to prospectively predict the risk of DR 15, 21."
  ]
}